    "bbox": [
      75,
      1829,
      695,
      1924
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "d) Ta tính $P(B|A) = \\frac{P(BA)}{P(A)} = \\frac{1124}{2250} = \\frac{562}{1125}$."
